{"article_id":"PID1rWZJZESUhgCs","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The deadly shooting at a newsroom in Annapolis , Md. , on Thursday was a `` targeted attack , ''","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"authorities said .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Acting Anne Arundel County Police Chief William Krampf told reporters at a news briefing Thursday evening","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"that the gunman entered the newsroom of the Capital Gazette with a shotgun","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"and scouted victims","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"as he walked through the building .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"`` This person was prepared today to come in .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"This person was prepared to shoot people .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"His intent was to cause harm , ''","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Krampf said .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"He added ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"`` We have no knowledge at all","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"that he was targeting anyone specific at the Capital . ''","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"BREAKING :","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"`` This was a targeted attack on the Capital Gazette , ''","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"authorities say .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"https : //t.co/IxnUmCJp0v","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"pic.twitter.com/rOlNhQ0835","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"- ABC News","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"( @ ABC )","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"June 29 , 2018","depth":4},{"id":21,"text":"At least five people were killed","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"and several others were injured on Thursday afternoon ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"after a man","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"wielding a long gun","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"opened fire on the Ann Arundel County newsroom of the Capital Gazette ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"authorities said .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Police also found what was initially thought to be an explosive device in the building ,","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"but Krampf later said","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"that it was determined to be smoke grenade canisters","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"used by the suspected shooter","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"when he entered the building .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"Police have arrested the suspected shooter ,","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"but have not yet released his identity","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"nor announced a motive for the attack .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"Krampf said","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"that there may be a possible connection to threats","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"made over social media as recently as Thursday .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"Those threats ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"he said ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"`` indicated violence . ''","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"`` We know","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"there were threats","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"sent to the Gazette through social media , ''","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"`` We ' re trying to confirm what account that was","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"and we ' re trying to confirm","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"who actually sent them . ''","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Krampf also pushed back on reports","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"that police turned to facial recognition software ,","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"because the suspect 's fingerprints were determined to be too damaged","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"or had been altered .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"`` Eventually his fingerprints will be taken , ''","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"`` I ' m going to be really clear about this guys .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"We have no information about facial recognition or anything about his fingerprints . ''","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":111,"left":76,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":68,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":57,"right":67,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":57,"left":0,"right